statements: SELECT * FROM quantum_communication_protocols;
SELECT protocol_id, protocol_name FROM quantum_communication_protocols;
SELECT * FROM quantum_communication_protocols WHERE quantum_bit_rate > 1000;
SELECT protocol_id, description FROM quantum_communication_protocols WHERE protocol_name = 'QKD';
SELECT protocol_id, protocol_name, quantum_bit_rate FROM quantum_communication_protocols ORDER BY quantum_bit_rate DESC;
SELECT protocol_name, description, quantum_bit_rate FROM quantum_communication_protocols;
SELECT * FROM quantum_communication_protocols WHERE quantum_bit_rate > 100 ORDER BY protocol_name DESC;
SELECT protocol_name, description FROM quantum_communication_protocols WHERE quantum_bit_rate < 50 AND LENGTH(description) > 20;
SELECT * FROM quantum_communication_protocols WHERE protocol_id IN (SELECT protocol_id FROM other_table WHERE condition);
SELECT DISTINCT protocol_name FROM quantum_communication_protocols ORDER BY protocol_name ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM QuantumProtocols;
SELECT protocol_name, description FROM QuantumProtocols ORDER BY protocol_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumProtocols WHERE protocol_id = 1;

SELECT protocol_name, data_content FROM QuantumProtocols JOIN ProtocolData ON QuantumProtocols.protocol_id = ProtocolData.protocol_id;
SELECT protocol_name, description FROM QuantumProtocols;
SELECT * FROM QuantumProtocols WHERE protocol_id = 1;
SELECT protocol_name, data_content->'fields' AS data_fields FROM QuantumProtocols JOIN ProtocolData ON QuantumProtocols.protocol_id = ProtocolData.protocol_id WHERE QuantumProtocols.protocol_id = 1;
SELECT protocol_id, data_content->'value' AS value FROM QuantumProtocols LEFT JOIN ProtocolData ON QuantumProtocols.protocol_id = ProtocolData.protocol_id WHERE ProtocolData.data_id IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM ProtocolData WHERE data_content->>'status' = 'active';

SELECT step_id, step_description FROM protocol_steps WHERE created_at > '2022-01-01';
SELECT metric_name, metric_value FROM protocol_metrics ORDER BY metric_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_protocols;
SELECT protocol_name, protocol_author FROM quantum_protocols WHERE created_at >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT protocol_name, protocol_description, COUNT(*) as total_steps FROM quantum_protocols JOIN protocol_steps ON quantum_protocols.protocol_id = protocol_steps.protocol_id GROUP BY protocol_name, protocol_description;
SELECT metric_name, AVG(metric_value) as avg_value FROM protocol_metrics GROUP BY metric_name ORDER BY avg_value DESC;
SELECT protocol_name, result_description, result_value FROM quantum_protocols JOIN protocol_results ON quantum_protocols.protocol_id = protocol_results.protocol_id WHERE result_value >= 0.5;
SELECT * FROM quantum_protocols;
SELECT protocol_id, protocol_name, creation_date FROM quantum_protocols ORDER BY protocol_id DESC;
SELECT device_name, manufacturer FROM quantum_devices WHERE protocol_id = 1;
SELECT parameter_name, value FROM quantum_parameters WHERE value > 0.5 ORDER BY value ASC;
SELECT username, email FROM users WHERE username LIKE 'a%';
SELECT protocol_name, description FROM quantum_protocols;
SELECT * FROM quantum_devices WHERE manufacturer = 'IBM';
SELECT protocol_name, COUNT(*) AS total_devices FROM quantum_protocols JOIN quantum_devices ON quantum_protocols.protocol_id = quantum_devices.protocol_id GROUP BY protocol_name;

SELECT users.username, quantum_protocols.protocol_name FROM users JOIN user_access ON users.user_id = user_access.user_id JOIN quantum_protocols ON user_access.protocol_id = quantum_protocols.protocol_id WHERE user_access.access_level > 1;

SELECT protocol_name, AVG(value) AS average_value FROM quantum_protocols JOIN quantum_parameters ON quantum_protocols.protocol_id = quantum_parameters.protocol_id GROUP BY protocol_name HAVING average_value > 0.5;
